OL,3,C'I haven't had a day off in 16 months'
OL,4,Csays unpaid full-time carer
OL,6,FA woman from Bristol is calling for
OL,7,Fmore be done to support unpaid carers
OL,8,Fafter her financial support was cut
OL,9,Fwhile caring full-time for her husband.
OL,11,FDorothy Cook, from Knowle, gave up
OL,12,Frunning her own business six years ago
OL,13,Fto look after Melvin, 77, who has a
OL,14,Fdegenerative brain disease known as
OL,15,Fataxia.
OL,17,FBut after his NHS care package was
OL,18,Fstopped, Dorothy told ITV News West
OL,19,FCountry she has not had a day off in
OL,20,Fsixteen months and is worried her own
OL,21,Fhealth is being impacted.
