OL,3,C'I haven't had a day off in 16 months'
OL,4,Csays unpaid full-time carer
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Bristol, North
OL,7,FSomerset and South Gloucestershire ICB
OL,8,Fsaid it has to make funding decisions
OL,9,Fbased on "a nationally set framework".
OL,11,FDorothy said: "I get nothing, I get
OL,12,Fnothing. Marvin gets disability
OL,13,Fallowance, but all our care packages
OL,14,Ffunding was removed.
OL,16,F"I haven't had a day off in sixteen
OL,17,Fmonths because they took the funding
OL,18,Ffor any respite. I thought unpaid
OL,19,Fcarers were supposed to get respite. I
OL,20,Fhaven't."
