OL,6,FMelvin was an electrical engineer who
OL,7,Fhelped design concorde. He loved
OL,8,Ftravelling and the outdoors, but in
OL,9,Fhis fifties he started to lose his
OL,10,Fbalance on walks and on bike rides.
OL,12,FIt took several years to get a
OL,13,Fdiagnosis of the rare brain disease
OL,14,Fataxia. More than a decade later he is
OL,15,Fbed-bound, struggles with his speech
OL,16,Fand relies on Dorothy for everything.
