OL,6,FDorothy said: "For him the hardest
OL,7,Fpart is watching me have to do it all
OL,8,Fas his carer because he feels guilty,
OL,9,Fhe feels upset, because he knows that
OL,10,Fhe's totally reliant on me. And
OL,11,Fwithout me there would be nobody else
OL,12,Fto care for him."
OL,14,FDorothy told ITV News West Country she
OL,15,Fis angry with the lack of support
OL,16,Favailable and says caring for her
OL,17,Fhusband has had a "massive impact" on
OL,18,Ftheir financial situation.
