OL,6,FCarer's UK now estimates 1.2 million
OL,7,Fcarers are in poverty. They said
OL,8,FDorothy's lack of support is not
OL,9,Funusual.
OL,11,FEmily Holzhausen, CBE, Director of
OL,12,FPolicy and Public Affairs at Carers
OL,13,FUK, said: "It's a real false economy
OL,14,Fif we don't support carers because
OL,15,Fthey end up with their own health
OL,16,Fissues and are more likely to be in
OL,17,Fpoor health than people who are not
OL,18,Fcaring.
